{"tid":1417044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄺仔：不認命 不分化 不放棄","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:14:12.000Z","uid":33989,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f3f6138bf60295e842d6070841905d3514acd51","tid":1417044,"uid":33989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mb7KAmVO3L4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMb7KAmVO3L4&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=1e70cf65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mb7KAmVO3L4</a><br />\n<br />\n鄺仔真係講得好岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由6月9號開始到而家<br />\n一樣訴求都無回應<br />\n開始有<span style=\"color: red;\">認命</span>嘅心態<br />\n和理非唔明行動升級（放火）嘅意義<br />\n比啲3毛乘虛而入<span style=\"color: red;\">分化</span><br />\n政府用想用冷處理對付今次返送中運動<br />\n一味靠拖<br />\n試圖令香港人慢慢<span style=\"color: red;\">放棄</span><br />\n<br />\n所以我哋除咗 不流血 不受傷 不被捕<br />\n我地仲要 <span style=\"color: red;\">不認命 不分化 不放棄</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地要比柒婆知 佢一日唔回應 我哋一日都會繼續落去！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec0833c2482021ca42dd2163277090b76da26717","tid":1417044,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8c9bd4ad3c85a149e7d7b1748d556d158b3fe64","tid":1417044,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔認命呀屌你 死都要你班撚屌同我地一齊攬炒"}]}